00:28:46,860 --> 00:28:49,500
Some wanted autographs, manuscripts

562
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:50,550
and also extra volumes.

563
00:29:28,750 --> 00:29:29,870
Chu Li.

564
00:29:30,190 --> 00:29:31,510
Come take a look.

565
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:35,380
What do you think
about this publicity banner?

566
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:37,120
[An oriental fantasy masterpiece
from best selling author Zhou Chuan]

567
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:38,220
[Book of Luo He God]

568
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:38,790
It's good.

569
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:39,750
Good.

570
00:30:05,030 --> 00:30:05,950
Hello?

571
00:30:05,950 --> 00:30:06,630
Chief Editor Yu.

572
00:30:06,630 --> 00:30:07,790
It's me, Zhou Chuan.

573
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:08,820
Hi, Mr Zhou Chuan.

574
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:09,670
Can I help you?

575
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:12,230
I just want to know.

576
00:30:12,230 --> 00:30:13,910
I've been trying to call my editor

577
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:15,870
about the online pre-sales of my book

578
00:30:15,870 --> 00:30:17,350
but I didn't get any response.

579
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,230
Is she alive?

580
00:30:20,910 --> 00:30:23,110
Mr Zhou Chuan,
your managing editor

581
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:24,310
is still alive.

582
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:26,750
[Online pre-sales is going well.
Please don't worry.]

583
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:27,990
[Chu Li]

584
00:30:28,150 --> 00:30:29,590
[must have been exhausted.]

585
00:30:29,990 --> 00:30:30,820
I'll remind her

586
00:30:30,820 --> 00:30:31,700
to check her phone.

587
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:33,580
I'm glad the online pre-sales
is going well.

588
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:35,190
All good now. Bye.

589
00:30:44,390 --> 00:30:45,110
Chu Li.

590
00:30:45,900 --> 00:30:47,550
Chief Editor.
Do you need anything?

591
00:30:47,710 --> 00:30:48,790
You must be tired.

592
00:30:49,230 --> 00:30:51,180
The online pre-sales is going well.

593
00:30:51,180 --> 00:30:52,230
You've worked hard.

594
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:53,390
Thanks, Chief Editor.

595
00:30:53,820 --> 00:30:55,630
You and Ah Xiang can go home now.

596
00:30:55,630 --> 00:30:56,830
Take a good rest.

597
00:30:58,340 --> 00:31:00,230
Oh, right.
You'd better check your phone.

598
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:04,820
[The subway is closed.]

599
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:16,520
[Not Drama King, it's Saviour]

600
00:31:04,820 --> 00:31:06,150
[Mr Zhou Chuan is hungry.]

601
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:07,950
[You probably need
to take a cab home tonight.]

602
00:31:07,950 --> 00:31:09,110
[An additional fee is incurred
if you take a cab at this hour.]

603
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,150
[You're still in the office?]

604
00:31:10,150 --> 00:31:11,150
[Are you still working
on the online pre-sales?]

605
00:31:11,150 --> 00:31:12,790
[Your risk of sudden death is increasing.]

606
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:14,110
[You have a nice bed at home]

607
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,310
[but you rather sleep in the office?]

608
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:16,470
[Are you out of your mind?]

609
00:31:27,790 --> 00:31:28,310
Miss.

610
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:29,390
Do you go to gym?

611
00:31:29,390 --> 00:31:30,830
Miss, I can give you a discount.

612
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:32,030
You don't look fat

613
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,190
but you can still strengthen your body.

614
00:31:33,190 --> 00:31:34,230
Our trainers are all award winners.

615
00:31:34,230 --> 00:31:34,830
No, thanks.

616
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:36,230
Our equipment are very good.

617
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:36,950
No, thanks.

618
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,390
Look at our facilities.

619
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:38,820
Look.

620
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:39,790
Stop pulling me.

621
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:41,580
Your fee is equivalent to
my monthly meal expenses.

622
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:42,710
Let me go.

623
00:31:44,390 --> 00:31:45,310
I'm sorry.

624
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,630
Why are you so rude?

625
00:31:46,630 --> 00:31:47,390
Just tell me if you're not interested.

626
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:48,620
Why did you push me?

627
00:31:48,620 --> 00:31:49,940
You used violence on me.

628
00:31:50,150 --> 00:31:51,230
You have to compensate me.

629
00:31:51,990 --> 00:31:53,590
Compensate?

630
00:31:53,870 --> 00:31:54,830
These papers

631
00:31:54,830 --> 00:31:55,870
probably cost 20 yuan.

632
00:31:55,870 --> 00:31:58,030
Do you want me to print a few hundred more
to build you a shelter?

633
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:59,060
These are colour prints.

634
00:31:59,060 --> 00:32:00,310
It costs me one and a half
for one piece of paper.

635
00:32:00,470 --> 00:32:01,150
So many pieces here.

636
00:32:01,150 --> 00:32:02,550
You have to pay me 300 yuan.

637
00:32:02,550 --> 00:32:03,510
If not, I'll call the cops.

638
00:32:03,510 --> 00:32:04,790
300 yuan?

639
00:32:05,390 --> 00:32:06,590
Call the cops then.

640
00:32:06,590 --> 00:32:08,590
I can sue you for extortion or something.

641
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:10,550
You...

642
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,310
Don't run.

643
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:12,310
You can't go if you don't pay.

644
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:13,260
Stop pulling me.

645
00:32:13,260 --> 00:32:14,350
Compensate me first.

646
00:32:48,710 --> 00:32:49,870
What's going on?

647
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:52,950
Get up.

648
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:57,230
I'm scared

649
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,070
just because you have company.

650
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:59,390
You still have to compensate me.

651
00:32:59,670 --> 00:33:00,430
Compensate...

652
00:33:01,110 --> 00:33:02,350
He hit him.

653
00:33:02,350 --> 00:33:03,150
He hit him.

654
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:11,830
Don't act on impulse in future.

655
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:14,350
Although the other party started it,

656
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,790
using violence in public

657
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:17,470
is still wrong.

658
00:33:18,230 --> 00:33:18,940
We got it.

659
00:33:18,940 --> 00:33:20,590
Thank you, Mr Policeman.

660
00:33:35,670 --> 00:33:36,220
Get on.

661
00:33:37,510 --> 00:33:38,150
I'll carry you on my back.

662
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:40,270
What?

663
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:41,230
Did you hurt your head too?

664
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:42,590
I said I'll carry you on my back.

665
00:33:42,590 --> 00:33:43,990
Did I not make myself clear?

666
00:33:46,590 --> 00:33:47,950
But...

667
00:34:01,950 --> 00:34:02,950
What is it now?

668
00:34:02,950 --> 00:34:03,990
Can you hurry up?

669
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:06,790
Don't let me squat here
in front of the police station.

670
00:34:16,350 --> 00:34:17,590
About that...

671
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:19,949
The online pre-sales is almost ready.

672
00:34:19,949 --> 00:34:22,750
We are just waiting for web support now.

673
00:34:22,750 --> 00:34:24,550
The circulation department
is working on it already.

674
00:34:27,469 --> 00:34:29,139
For the exclusive giveaways,

675
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:31,030
what do you think we should give?

676
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:32,150
Autograph?

677
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:34,830
Autograph might not be that attractive.

678
00:34:35,550 --> 00:34:36,830
Not attractive?

679
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:41,150
How about lucky draw for forwarded post?

680
00:34:41,150 --> 00:34:42,949
This is very important.

681
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:45,420
Do you have any private item?

682
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:49,830
Private item?

683
00:34:52,989 --> 00:34:54,469
My editor's head.

684
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:04,710
Oh, right. Mr Zhou Chuan.

685
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:07,150
Why were you on the street today?

686
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:09,230
You weren't even walking the dog.

687
00:35:10,590 --> 00:35:11,750
I was on my way

688
00:35:11,750 --> 00:35:12,700
to the convenience store.

689
00:35:13,260 --> 00:35:14,270
Nothing odd about that.

690
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:23,820
Why don't we take a cab...

691
00:35:54,470 --> 00:35:56,590
[Chu Li, don't forget our appointment]

692
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:59,520
[Flying Elephant]

693
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:58,260
[with the printing house
tomorrow evening.]

694
00:36:04,490 --> 00:36:09,770
[Flying Elephant]

695
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:07,430
[I won't go the office tomorrow morning.]

696
00:36:07,430 --> 00:36:09,030
[Mr Zhou Chuan wants to
have a meeting with me]

697
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,630
[about the exclusive giveaways.]

698
00:36:09,770 --> 00:36:10,650
[Chu Li]

699
00:36:13,270 --> 00:36:14,150
Get up.

700
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:15,790
Disinfect your wound before you sleep.

701
00:36:16,030 --> 00:36:17,230
You'll get an infection if you don't.

702
00:36:23,430 --> 00:36:24,660
If you don't get up now,

703
00:36:24,660 --> 00:36:26,670
I'll pull out your pants.

704
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:31,230
Don't think that you can get away

705
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:32,550
with your good looks and writing skills.

706
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:34,670
I'll call the cops

707
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:37,310
if you do something to me when I'm asleep.

708
00:36:38,590 --> 00:36:39,790
I just want you to get up

709
00:36:39,790 --> 00:36:41,670
and take off your pants.

710
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:45,270
What?

711
00:36:45,270 --> 00:36:46,630
You have to disinfect that knee.

712
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:48,100
You have been out all day.

713
00:36:48,100 --> 00:36:49,350
Are you going to fall asleep
with all that?

714
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,060
Alright, I got it.

715
00:36:52,060 --> 00:36:53,590
I can't take off my pants with you here.

716
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:55,030
Go downstairs now.

717
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:56,670
I'll take them off once you're gone.

718
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,390
You can't fool me with that.

719
00:36:59,390 --> 00:37:00,470
It's a trick to get me out

720
00:37:00,470 --> 00:37:01,550
so that you can continue sleeping,
isn't it?

721
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,390
No, no.

722
00:37:02,390 --> 00:37:04,030
You go out first. I'll take them off.

723
00:37:04,430 --> 00:37:05,350
Alright?

724
00:37:06,310 --> 00:37:07,430
I'll come up to check in a while.

725
00:37:08,750 --> 00:37:10,070
You sound like

726
00:37:10,070 --> 00:37:11,150
a teacher

727
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:13,180
checking on a student's homework.

728
00:37:13,180 --> 00:37:14,470
Go now.

729
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:27,550
Hello?

730
00:37:27,550 --> 00:37:28,630
Buddy.

731
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:34,070
What got into you?

732
00:37:34,070 --> 00:37:35,430
I'm not used to this.

733
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,150
What's the matter?

734
00:37:36,430 --> 00:37:38,230
I think I'm undergoing puberty.

735
00:37:39,550 --> 00:37:40,550
What happened?

736
00:37:41,950 --> 00:37:43,910
I suddenly realize
the deep physical meaning

737
00:37:43,910 --> 00:37:46,230
in gender distinction of mankind.

738
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:47,510
Man

739
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,870
and woman.

740
00:37:49,870 --> 00:37:51,790
I don't understand.

741
00:37:51,790 --> 00:37:53,630
It's tiring to explain to you.

742
00:37:56,830 --> 00:37:58,070
Go downstairs to apply medicine

743
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:59,670
and come back up to bed.

744
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:01,070
You can sleep in tomorrow.

745
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,190
I've applied leave for you.

746
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:04,460
Just go to the printing house
in the evening.

747
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:07,470
Why are you fixing my schedule?

748
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:10,230
Flying Elephant texted you.

749
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,310
You looked at my phone?

750
00:38:12,790 --> 00:38:14,630
The message popped up
according to your setting.

751
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:16,150
I can't unseen it.

752
00:38:16,630 --> 00:38:17,710
Since I've seen it,

753
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:19,310
I decided to apply leave for you.

754
00:38:19,310 --> 00:38:20,150
What's the problem?

755
00:38:21,430 --> 00:38:23,700
This did sound like me.

756
00:38:24,430 --> 00:38:25,750
I guessed it right.

757
00:38:25,750 --> 00:38:26,510
You

758
00:38:26,510 --> 00:38:28,470
always talk behind my back
with your colleagues.

759
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:30,270
"Mr Zhou Chuan is running late again."

760
00:38:30,270 --> 00:38:31,670
"Who does he think he is?"

761
00:38:31,670 --> 00:38:32,940
"The centre of the universe?"

762
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:36,350
You added that last one.

763
00:38:39,630 --> 00:38:40,750
Your leg.

764
00:38:46,910 --> 00:38:48,030
Stop jumping.

765
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:49,350
The stairs will collapse.

766
00:38:49,350 --> 00:38:51,150
Don't you know you are heavy?

767
00:38:52,420 --> 00:38:53,670
I must thank you for your trouble

768
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:56,030
to carry me home then.

769
00:38:56,380 --> 00:38:57,470
I'm glad you know.

770
00:39:00,510 --> 00:39:01,510
Get on.

771
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:05,150
Since I've started a good deed,
let me carry you down.

772
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:08,990
Thank you, Mr Zhou Chuan.

773
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:15,670
Go slow.

774
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:17,270
You pulled an all nighter

775
00:39:17,270 --> 00:39:18,310
just for that 350 thousand.

776
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:21,390
If you don't hit that target,

777
00:39:21,390 --> 00:39:23,390
you have to carry me
around the neighbourhood.

778
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,750
I don't want to.

779
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:27,830
Be gentle.

780
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:44,750
Are you making some embroidery?

781
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:46,270
At this rate,

782
00:39:46,270 --> 00:39:47,660
it will take you forever.

783
00:39:48,390 --> 00:39:49,230
Let me do it.

784
00:39:49,950 --> 00:39:51,670
You know how to treat wounds?

785
00:40:01,620 --> 00:40:02,750
I attended first aid training.

786
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:08,830
Thank you, Mr Zhou Chuan.

787
00:40:09,310 --> 00:40:10,590
You really don't want to slit the wound

788
00:40:10,590 --> 00:40:11,990
to check for residues?

789
00:40:12,350 --> 00:40:14,030
What if the wound heals

790
00:40:14,030 --> 00:40:15,310
with the residue still inside?

791
00:40:18,070 --> 00:40:19,830
Let me do it myself.

792
00:40:40,580 --> 00:40:41,710
Eight Treasure Congee?

793
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:50,670
Why is it so salty?

794
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:53,950
Mr Zhou Chuan.

795
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:54,790
I'm really sorry

796
00:40:54,790 --> 00:40:55,950
I got up late this morning

797
00:40:55,950 --> 00:40:57,510
and did not make you breakfast.

798
00:40:57,510 --> 00:40:58,180
Oh, right.

799
00:40:58,180 --> 00:40:59,670
Give me the phone number
of this take-out restaurant.

800
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:00,990
I want to file a complaint.

801
00:41:00,990 --> 00:41:02,700
Food has dignity too.

802
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,110
This Eight Treasure Congee
is supposed to be sweet.

803
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:05,910
This is salty and inedible.

804
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,070
I made this.

805
00:41:08,790 --> 00:41:09,950
You made this?

806
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:20,830
Actually, it won't be salty

807
00:41:20,830 --> 00:41:22,630
after adding hot water.

808
00:41:24,910 --> 00:41:26,190
Then you should have more.

809
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:28,950
Eight Treasure Congee can boost your qi
and nourish your blood.

810
00:41:28,950 --> 00:41:30,950
It's perfect for hard workers like you.

811
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:35,070
You made this congee just for me?

812
00:41:35,790 --> 00:41:36,750
Yes.

813
00:41:36,750 --> 00:41:38,990
I'm afraid if you work yourself to death,

814
00:41:38,990 --> 00:41:40,390
no one can help me
hit the 350 thousand target.

815
00:41:42,990 --> 00:41:44,550
I knew it.

816
00:41:53,990 --> 00:41:55,470
Hello? Chief Editor Yu.

817
00:41:56,470 --> 00:41:57,380
Really?

818
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:58,790
I'll tell him now.

819
00:41:59,580 --> 00:42:00,870
Good news.

820
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:02,630
Pre-sales of your book starts next week.

821
00:42:02,870 --> 00:42:05,300
I'll hashtag you
on all official platforms.

822
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:06,350
You must forward them out.

823
00:42:06,350 --> 00:42:07,910
The more the better.

824
00:42:08,380 --> 00:42:10,030
I'll have to pass this congee.

825
00:42:10,030 --> 00:42:11,270
I need to go to the printing house now.

826
00:42:15,630 --> 00:42:17,670
It's really too salty.

827
00:42:19,550 --> 00:42:21,430
I've booked a cab for you.

828
00:42:21,430 --> 00:42:22,270
I'll pay for it.

829
00:42:28,550 --> 00:42:29,630
Goodbye.
